OL,3,C#20,000 reward to catch arsonist who
OL,4,Ckilled seven-year-old boy
OL,6,FA #20,000 reward has been offered to
OL,7,Fcatch an arsonist who killed a seven-
OL,8,Fyear-old boy 28 years ago.
OL,10,FJoe McCafferty was at his aunt's house
OL,11,Fin Haywood Avenue, Huddersfield, for a
OL,12,Fsleepover on 2 May 1997 when flammable
OL,13,Fliquid was poured through the
OL,14,Fletterbox and set alight.
OL,16,FHe was taken to hospital with his
OL,17,Fbrother Nicky, but died a short time
OL,18,Flater.
