OL,6,FThe first arrests in the case came in
OL,7,F2015 when a 65-year-old man and 60-
OL,8,Fyear-old woman were arrested before
OL,9,Fbeing released without charge.
OL,11,FCharity Crimestoppers is now offering
OL,12,F#20,000 for information to help solve
OL,13,Fthe case.
OL,15,FSenior investigating officer Det Ch
OL,16,FInsp Damian Roebuck: "From the outset
OL,17,Fof this investigation we have firmly
OL,18,Fbelieved that the answers to this
OL,19,Fhorrendous crime would be found in the
OL,20,FHuddersfield area.
