OL,3,C#20,000 reward to catch arsonist who
OL,4,Ckilled seven-year-old boy
OL,6,F"It is now 28 years since Joe's life
OL,7,Fwas taken so cruelly and so suddenly,
OL,8,Fand we remain committed to finding
OL,9,Fthose responsible, so Joe's family can
OL,10,Fget the justice that they deserve.
OL,12,F"My message to the people of
OL,13,FHuddersfield is clear ` if you have
OL,14,Fany information about who was
OL,15,Fresponsible for the fire then please
OL,16,Fcome forward."
OL,18,FCrimestoppers regional manager Gemma
OL,19,FGibbs said: "We encourage anyone who
OL,20,Fholds even the smallest piece of
OL,21,Finformation to come forward.
